reviewText: It just wasn't as funny as I thought it would be.
The DVD was new and a quality product. The cost ratio is very good. I would recommend buying this product to anyone interested in buying a very good Christian comedy DVD!
I was so excited to see a dvd without cussing. I bought both vol 1 and 2. It was good to see these different comedians doing their thing on stage cracking jokes, clean jokes!
enjoying my order love your business and service, description and item just like was posted loving it getting ready to get new pair.
It's not as funny as I thought that it would be.  I thought that another comedian would perform, but he didn't...

It was really refreshing to be able to laugh and not have to censor the language.  This dvd can be enjoyed by families, although some of the jokes are context-specific (black church) most individuals will enjoy at least a portion of the dvd.  Give it a shot you just may laugh 'til it hurts.
I received the product as promised, however I did not find the comedy to be funny. I would not recommend it to anyone.
This DVD is very funny.  Some of the comedians were hilarious. This DVD is definitely worth having in your family video collection for good clean comedy.
I was laughing the whole way through.  I have finally found a show I can watch with my kids and grandmother... and  we all laughed until we cried.  I hope they come out with another one, and soon.
